{"tid":2253731,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"沒揹背囊卻遭警指背囊藏士巴拿 女生管有非法工具罪名不成立 男被告堵路罪名亦不成立","createTime":"2020-10-22T10:52:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T11:55:09.000Z","uid":240362,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f36fb170f63cd6f11357f1b6de13d637b6835366","tid":2253731,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:52:51.000Z","msg":"去年11月市民連日發起「大三罷」行動，其間有人在沙田科學園附近堵路，多人被捕。當中女學生及售貨員否認阻礙公眾地方罪，女生另涉藏士巴拿而被加控一罪。案件早前審結，裁判官李志豪今裁決時明言，警員證供出錯，既聲稱在女生背囊內搜出士巴拿，惟影片卻顯示女生案發時根本沒揹背囊，故裁定她面對的管有非法工具罪名不成立，惟堵路罪成。另一方面，警員在沒施行警誡下查問男被告，對他不公，遂剔除其招認口供，並裁定男被告堵路罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n李官將案件押後至下月17日判刑，以待索取女被告的感化及社會服務令報告，其間續准保釋，但表明所有判刑可能性均存在，須視乎報告內容而定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201022/UACQF46DEVHHNL3PRVTYI6ARTI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201022%2FUACQF46DEVHHNL3PRVTYI6ARTI%2F&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPWvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=aad12d99\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201022%2FUACQF46DEVHHNL3PRVTYI6ARTI%2F&h=16df4db6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201022/UACQF46DEVHHNL3PRVTYI6ARTI/</a>"},{"pid":"3eb486fb79b634d112a6530e5737c0d827604c45","tid":2253731,"uid":219969,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:53:49.000Z","msg":"荒撚謬，又鳩作證供冇後果"},{"pid":"eb4d22c03a038e9baa4f9bba046b7eb8ea07a2bf","tid":2253731,"uid":168389,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:58:22.000Z","msg":"假口供 生豬肉 無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"691472a7679916004772ed21e7a48a6b44791d13","tid":2253731,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3eb486fb79b634d112a6530e5737c0d827604c45","tid":2253731,"uid":219969,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:53:49.000Z","msg":"荒撚謬，又鳩作證供冇後果"},"citedBy"